Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.05,0:22:38.59,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Sweet love in love world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.91,0:22:42.49,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Sweet love in love world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.96,0:22:47.05,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}You know what you wanna be
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.58,0:23:13.69,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}永遠のうた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:19.65,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}歌唱無盡的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.53,0:21:27.55,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}儘管愛不忍釋  心有淒楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.99,0:21:29.11,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.39,0:21:35.31,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}仍因為無法遏制而厭惡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.27,0:21:44.57,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}即使我就在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.77,0:21:54.95,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}映入眼簾的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.23,0:22:00.47,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不盡相同
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.67,0:22:12.03,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}心意  未來  笑容
